data.description: Welcome to your new home, where timeless Spanish-style architecture meets modern upgrades and an ideal location. This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts a bonus room that can serve as an office, nursery, or whatever your heart desires. Located in a convenient neighborhood, this property offers you the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility. This home was thoughtfully rejuvenated with a fresh coat of paint just seven months ago, ensuring a vibrant and welcoming curb appeal. The heart of the home, your kitchen, is adorned with a plethora of solid oak cabinets. Recently, it received a makeover with a new gas stove top, a brand-new fridge, updated sink and faucets, a new RO system, resurfaced countertops, black appliances, and fresh tile flooring. It's the ideal space for culinary enthusiasts and gatherings. Luxury vinyl flooring graces most of the wet areas, harmonizing with elegant tile flooring, creating a seamless and low-maintenance interior.: Enjoy the benefits of a new water softener and purification system, ensuring the highest quality water for you and your family. The backyard is a canvas ready for your personal touch. Set on a generous lot, this open space allows you to create your outdoor sanctuary. Imagine lush gardens, a serene patio, or even a sparkling pool - the possibilities are endless. Less than half a mile to the freeway, you'll have easy access to the entire Valley, making your daily commute a breeze. With a newer HVAC system and water heater, you can be confident in the efficiency and comfort of your new home. Don't miss this opportunity to make this Spanish-style gem your very own. Whether you're looking for a place to raise a family, work from home, or entertain friends and loved ones, this property has it all. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the magic of this home in person. Your dream lifestyle awaits!
